snippet.title: ColdFusion
snippet.description:
Hi, welcome to ColdFusion (formerly known as ColdfusTion). My name is Dagogo Altraide and I create and narrate all the videos on here.

This channel aims to let you experience the cutting edge of the world around us in a relaxed atmosphere where you can feel at home and have fun. 
Learn the histories and some interesting facts about some of the worlds biggest companies such as Samsung, Facebook, Google, Apple, Tesla and more.
Did you know Samsung has a military defense division?
Did you know Tesla cars are starting to learn how to drive?
Did you know Steve Jobs didn't know how to code when he first met Steve Wozniak?
There's plenty of useful information here, so be sure to subscribe so you can see it all!

Contact | *Business ONLY* dagogoa@gmail.com

Join the fun on: 

@ColdFusion_TV

Facebook | www.facebook.com/coldfusiontv

G+ | gplus.to/ColdfusTion
